defaultThe CWU has rejected Royal Mail’s proposals and is exploring the legality of the compan
defaulty’s
default proposals. The union intends
default to approach th
defaulte European Commission to seek its view on the legality of the move, given the link to its approval of state aid. The union further believes the issue should be raised in Parliament and be subject to an appropriate inquiry.
